{"tid":968354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新年第一天　他在家門外被墜毀直升機砸死","createTime":"2019-01-04T07:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T08:53:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6e61593413c1542b2d745a0fa8e40071e561df","tid":968354,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:27:53.000Z","msg":"巴西一名男子在新年第一天就遭遇死劫。該男子周二和父親喝完咖啡走出家門後，突然被一架墜落的觀光直升機擊中，當場慘死路邊。<br />\n該起意外發生在聖保羅市濱海小鎮烏巴圖巴（Ubatuba）。一架觀光直升機正載著一對夫妻觀光客起飛空中遊覽時，直升機一起飛就狀況有異，機師努力穩住機身，然仍於起飛不久後往地面墜落，整個過程全被機上乘客用手機拍下。<br />\n直升機墜毀時不幸擊中路人、42歲的萊特（Alessandro Correia Leite）。萊特當場身亡，機上的2名觀光客僅受輕傷，機師則是毫髮無傷。<br />\n萊特父親尼托（Antonio Correa Leite Neto）表示，意外發生前，他和兒子才剛在家裡喝咖啡：「我和他喝了一杯咖啡。他喝完後出門，而我則是回房間休息。」沒想到兒子踏出門不久，他聽見直升機墜毀聲音，立刻跑出家門查看，發現有人傷亡，還要另一個孩子趕快報警。尼托說：「我走近觀察，但一開始沒發現那是我兒子。」<br />\n警方目前正在調查墜機原因。直升機所屬公司表示，對於致命意外感到十分不幸，將盡全力協助死者家屬。（桂家齊／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idwAfqt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidwAfqt.png&h=90cdeef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BmSvOLu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmSvOLu.png&h=2ffe163c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GpJOAqw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGpJOAqw.png&h=19720c4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190104/1494600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190104%2F1494600&d=JS6%2Bb5RV8sKIbXK7uPI%2FUP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=8ede0699\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190104%2F1494600&h=423319f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190104/1494600</a>"},{"pid":"b287d987ee353237d5911948913e7902ed8c7378","tid":968354,"uid":12201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:30:45.000Z","msg":"死劫難逃"},{"pid":"f802f4d92f2e0ebd21cec836210f48ec3087a38a","tid":968354,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:21:45.000Z","msg":"死神來了"},{"pid":"66bc6a2bd8977f10a02268e8856d25eb2f663fe6","tid":968354,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/org1bng.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Forg1bng.gif&h=123ef102&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"478ea8dc3f5c703757ff6e63670dac2188cb4be1","tid":968354,"uid":12554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"Donnie Darko"}]}